    <div class="content"><p>Friends and Dr. Kim</p>
<p>As a 25 yr. long soyless vegan, I eat both for taste and nutrition.  Over these long years I have learned the hard way that beans must be properly prepared or else.  Soaking garbs for 24 hrs is essential.  Boiling for an hour is also essential.  Also essential is to cook them for many hours for digestibility.</p>
<p>to your improved health</p>
